messages.message: my suspicion is that, at this point, we cannot run any notebooks on production due to this error

Then I went into file explorer and that again gave me an exception from file-service stating file not found. I did a refresh in file explorer and the file was there
Thanks @Gunjan! Can you share what exeption you saw?
I don't remember it clearly, but I think that was file not found for the file that I was trying to rename. This happened somewhere around 12 PM IST
As the file was showing with the new name in file explorer, after two exceptions, I ignored it at that moment
